Vishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%2C%20one%20of%20the%20lawyers%20for%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid-Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20matter%2C%20said%20that%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Varanasi%20district%20court%20had%20been%20complied%20with.%20A%20pujari%20of%20the%20Shri%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Mandir%20Trust%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%2C%20conducted%20the%20%E2%80%9Cshayan%20arti%E2%80%9D%20after%20%E2%80%9Cputting%20up%20idols%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20said%20Jain.%20Another%20lawyer%20for%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%2C%20Saurabh%20Tiwari%2C%20too%20confirmed%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAn%20Akhand%20Jyoti%20started%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20Daily%20Arti%20of%20all%20above%20deities%20%E2%80%93%20Morning%20Mangla%20Arti%2C%20Bhog%20Arti%2C%20evening%20arti%2C%20late%20sunset%20evening%20arti%2C%20Shayan%20arti%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jain%20said.%20Jain%20said%20so%20far%20two%20aartis%20had%20been%20conducted%20at%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20claimed%20by%20the%20Hindu%20side%20to%20be%20the%20%E2%80%9CVyas%20cellar%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20would%20be%20five%20aarti%20sessions%20daily%2C%20added%20Jain%3A%20the%20first%20one%20at%203%3A30%20am%2C%20followed%20by%2012%20pm%20(bhog)%2C%204%20pm%2C%207%20pm%20and%2010%3A30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%20also%20shared%20photos%20of%20the%20puja%20inside%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20district%20judge%20Ajaya%20Krishna%20Vishesha%20on%20January%2031%20%E2%80%93%20his%20last%20working%20day%20before%20retirement%20%E2%80%93%20allowed%20Hindus%20to%20worship%20inside%20a%20sealed%20basement%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20and%20police%20stepped%20in%20to%20secure%20the%20area%20late%20at%20night%20and%20removed%20the%20barricading%20on%20the%20southern%20end%20of%20the%20mosque.%20The%20mosque%20had%20been%20barricaded%20for%20the%20last%20three%20decades%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20and%20police%20have%20refused%20to%20divulge%20details%20and%20responded%20through%20cryptic%20statements%20on%20the%20compliance%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20the%20intervening%20hours%20of%20January%2031%20and%20February%201%2C%20Varanasi%20district%20magistrate%20S.%20Rajalingam%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20compliance%20of%20the%20order%20of%20the%20court%20had%20been%20done%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DM%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20provide%20details%20or%20answer%20queries%20on%20the%20breaking%20of%20the%20barricades.%20What%20transpired%20inside%20the%20cellar%20with%20the%20entry%20of%20the%20administration%20following%20the%20court%20order%20is%20not%20yet%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20General%20of%20Police%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Prashant%20Kumar%20said%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20has%20been%20followed%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%20that%20there%20was%20sufficient%20police%20security%20at%20the%20site.%20The%20atmosphere%20is%20not%20tense%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01162611%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-01-at-3.21.04-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221132%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01162611%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-01-at-3.21.04-PM.jpeg%201132w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01162611%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-01-at-3.21.04-PM-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01162611%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-01-at-3.21.04-PM-1024x682.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695251%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22754%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHindu%20prayers%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque.%20Photo%3A%20Vishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%20on%20X%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20judge%20Vishesha%20on%20January%2031%20directed%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20make%20arrangements%20for%20puja%20and%20other%20Hindu%20activities%20inside%20the%20southern%20%3Cem%3Etehkhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(cellar)%20of%20the%20mosque%20within%20seven%20days.%20Judge%20Vishvesha%20directed%20the%20administration%20to%20conduct%20the%20puja%20and%20%E2%80%9Crag-bhog%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cidols%E2%80%9D%20inside%20the%20tehkhana%20through%20a%20pujari%20appointed%20by%20the%20Shri%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Varanasi%20court%20order%20came%20days%20after%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fasis-survey-report-says-a-large-hindu-temple-existed-under-the-gyanvapi-mosque%5C%22%3Ein%20its%20survey%20report%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%3C%2Fa%3E%20claimed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20Hindu%20temple%E2%80%9D%20existed%20there%20prior%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20existing%20structure%20(the%20mosque)%20and%20that%20parts%20of%20the%20temple%20were%20modified%20and%20used%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Islamic%20place%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20who%20are%20seeking%20religious%20rights%20within%20the%20mosque%20as%20well%20as%20its%20ultimate%20possession%20from%20Muslims%2C%20dubbed%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20as%20a%20victory%20and%20equated%20it%20to%20the%20controversial%20unlocking%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201986.%20The%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20eventually%20demolished%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20Hindu%20activists%20assembled%20at%20the%20call%20of%20members%20of%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretakers%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20said%20the%20district%20court%20passed%20the%20order%20based%20on%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20Hindu%20side%20without%20seeking%20any%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20passed%20the%20order%20on%20an%20application%20filed%20by%20a%20local%20priest%20Shailendra%20Kumar%20Pathak%20of%20the%20Acharya%20Ved%20Vyas%20Peeth%20temple%2C%20who%20had%20sought%20rights%20to%20worship%20the%20Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%20and%20other%20alleged%20visible%20and%20invisible%20deities%20he%20claimed%20were%20in%20the%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretakers%20of%20the%20mosque%20rejected%20all%20claims%20made%20by%20Pathak%20that%20there%20were%20idols%20kept%20inside%20the%20previously-sealed%20cellar%20and%20that%20his%20ancestors%20used%20to%20carry%20out%20puja%20inside%20the%20cellar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Vishvesha%2C%20however%2C%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiff%2C%20and%20directed%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20make%20necessary%20iron%20fencing%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20puja.%20The%20district%20magistrate%20had%20on%20January%2024%20completed%20the%20process%20of%20taking%20over%20the%20cellar%20after%20the%20court%20on%20January%2017%20directed%20the%20district%20magistrate%20to%20keep%20the%20cellar%20secure%20and%20appointed%20him%20as%20the%20receiver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20application%2C%20Pathak%20claimed%20that%20there%20were%20idols%20kept%20in%20the%20southern%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20that%20his%20ancestors%20as%20priests%20conducted%20worship%20of%20the%20idols%20kept%20there.%20However%2C%20Pathak%20further%20claimed%2C%20%E2%80%9CPujari%20Vyas%20ji%2C%E2%80%9D%20or%20Somnath%20Vyas%2C%20his%20maternal%20grandfather%2C%20was%20prevented%20from%20entering%20the%20barricaded%20area%20of%20the%20mosque%20after%20December%201993.%20The%20rag-bhog%20and%20sanskar%20rituals%20were%20also%20stopped%2C%20Pathak%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20ancient%20Hindu%20idols%20and%20several%20other%20religious%20items%20linked%20to%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20were%20inside%20the%20cellar.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20necessary%20to%20carry%20out%20regular%20puja%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emurtis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(idols)%20inside%20the%20tehkhana%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20of%20Management%2C%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masajid%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%2C%20vehemently%20denied%20the%20claims%20in%20court.%20The%20committee%20in%20written%20applications%20told%20the%20court%20that%20no%20member%20of%20the%20Vyas%20family%20ever%20carried%20out%20puja%20in%20the%20cellar.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20question%20of%20stopping%20someone%20from%20conducting%20puja%20from%20December%201993%20does%20not%20arise%2C%20the%20committee%20said.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20alleged%20idol%20was%20ever%20present%20at%20the%20site%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20committee%20said%20and%20denied%20the%20claims%20of%20Pathak%20that%20his%20family%20had%20ancestral%20occupation%20of%20the%20cellar.%20The%20cellar%20has%20always%20been%20under%20the%20occupation%20of%20the%20mosque%20committee%2C%20the%20caretakers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES.M.%20Yasin%2C%20joint%20secretary%20of%20the%20masjid%20committee%2C%20rejected%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20Hindu%20side%20and%20said%20that%20no%20puja%20had%20ever%20been%20held%20in%20the%20tehkhana%20and%20that%20there%20are%20no%20idols%20there.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20only%20bamboo%20poles%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20all%20lies.%20They%20have%20no%20evidence.%20The%20court%20passed%20the%20order%20without%20any%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yasin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYasin%20also%20questioned%20why%20the%20judge%20did%20not%20seek%20a%20factual%20position%20from%20the%20district%20administration%20which%20had%20sealed%20the%20cellar%20and%20barricaded%20the%20premises%20in%201995%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cellar%20has%20always%20been%20in%20our%20possession%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yasin%2C%20who%20objected%20to%20the%20breach%20of%20the%20old%20barricade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyers%20of%20the%20Muslim%20side%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Deen%20Mohammad%20suit%20of%201937%20did%20not%20make%20any%20mention%20of%20Vyas%20family%20occupying%20the%20tehkhana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20The%20Wire%2C%20Pathak%20was%20overjoyed%20at%20the%20compliance%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20first%20step.%20But%20this%20is%20nothing%20new%20as%20puja%20used%20to%20be%20held%20even%20earlier.%20Now%2C%20the%20baricadding%20has%20been%20removed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathak%20says%20the%20ultimate%20aim%20is%20to%20take%20over%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20%E2%80%9Crestore%E2%80%9D%20it%20to%20a%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathak%20claimed%20that%20till%20the%20age%20of%2015%20he%20would%20enter%20the%20basement%20to%20conduct%20puja%20with%20his%20grandfather%20Somnath%20Vyas%2C%20who%20was%20also%20the%20one%20who%20filed%20the%20original%20suit%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20matter%20seeking%20claim%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathak%20claimed%20that%20idols%20of%20six-seven%20deities%2C%20including%20a%20shiv%20ling%2C%20used%20to%20be%20worshipped%20inside%20the%20basement%20before%20it%20was%20sealed%20and%20barricaded%20following%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20in%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706785040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01162350%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-01-at-3.21.03-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fvaranasi-district-admin-oversees-hindu-prayers-inside-basement-of-gyanvapi-mosque%22%2C%22