20meet%20Hardman%20for%20the%20first%20time%20over%20Zoom%20in%20January%2C%20four%20days%20after%20the%20release%20of%20his%20new%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BCharles%20III%3A%20New%20King.%20New%20Court.%20The%20Inside%20Story%2C%26quot%3B%20published%20on%20January%2018.%20(In%20the%20US%2C%20it's%20retitled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.simonandschuster.com%2Fbooks%2FThe-Making-of-a-King%2FRobert-Hardman%2F9781639365319%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Making%20of%20a%20King%3A%20King%20Charles%20III%20and%20the%20Modern%20Monarchy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20looks%20polished%20in%20a%20crisp%20white%20shirt%20and%20a%20teal-printed%20tie.%20His%20face%20is%20framed%20with%20his%20signature%20square-shaped%20glasses%20as%20he%20recounts%20his%20royal%20career%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20according%20to%20Hardman%2C%20happened%20completely%20by%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHardman%20didn't%20intend%20to%20become%20a%20royal%20correspondent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHardman%20was%20working%20as%20a%20columnist%20and%20news%20reporter%20at%20the%20Daily%20Telegraph%20in%20London%20when%2C%20in%20January%20of%201992%2C%20he%20was%20sent%20on%20a%20travel%20assignment%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-crown-swiss-ski-resort-prince-charles-avalanche-accident-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKlosters%2C%20a%20luxury%20ski%20resort%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Swiss%20Alps%20that%20doubles%20as%20a%20billionaire's%20playground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20only%20brief%20was%20to%20find%20some%20%26quot%3Bskiing%20stories%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me.%20He%20ended%20up%20finding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsarah-ferguson-says-skin-cancer-diagnosis-was-shock-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESarah%2C%20Duchess%20of%20York%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20off%20I%20went%20with%20a%20photographer%2C%20and%20while%20we%20were%20there%2C%20we%20stumbled%20across%20the%20Duchess%20of%20York%20and%20her%20daughters%2C%20who%20were%20having%20one%20of%20those%20royal%20photo%20calls%20on%20the%20Alps%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20hill%2C%26quot%3B%20Hardman%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221815%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Duchess%20Of%20York%20with%20Princess%20Beatrice%20and%20Princess%20Eugenie%20in%20Klosters%20in%20January%201992%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65af959543bb77284b9f9b04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221361%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Duchess%20Of%20York%20with%20Princess%20Beatrice%20and%20Princess%20Eugenie%20in%20Klosters%20in%20January%201992.%3Cp%3ETim%20Graham%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHardman%20didn't%20know%20it%20then%2C%20but%201992%20was%20set%20to%20be%20a%20grisly%20year%20in%20royal%20history%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%26quot%3Bannus%20horribilis%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II%20called%20it%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royal.uk%2Fannus-horribilis-speech%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enow-famous%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20marking%20her%20Ruby%20Jubilee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrince%20Charles%2C%20Prince%20Andrew%2C%20and%20Princess%20Anne%20ended%20their%20respective%20marriages%2C%20and%20the%20royal%20family's%20largest%20residence%2C%20Windsor%20Castle%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-crown-season-5-episode-4-annus-horribilis-speech-explained-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseverely%20damaged%20in%20a%20fire%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20years%20that%20have%20followed%20have%20been%20just%20as%20tumultuous%2C%20particularly%20for%20the%20king.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20king's%20shadow%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHardman%20tells%20me%20he%20was%20inspired%20to%20write%20his%20new%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BCharles%20III%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20making%20the%20BBC%20documentary%20about%20the%20first%20year%20o