%20house-sitting%20when%20my%20sister%20tried%20it%20after%20responding%20to%20a%20classified%20advert%20in%20The%20Lady%20magazine.%20I%20loved%20the%20idea%20of%20house-sitting%20and%20living%20like%20a%20local%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20some%20research%20on%20the%20internet%20and%20found%20Trusted%20Housesitters%2C%20a%20website%20that%20sets%20people%20up%20with%20house-sitters%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20paid%2C%20but%20I%20would%20stay%20in%20their%20homes%20for%20free%20in%20return%20for%20looking%20after%20the%20owner's%20pets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20house-sitting%20after%20I%20retired%20to%20fill%20my%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%20in%202014%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20retire%20and%20wanted%20to%20start%20house-sitting%20to%20fill%20my%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rented%20out%20my%20house%20in%20Denver%20through%20an%20agent.%20The%20rent%20would%20cover%20my%20mortgage%20and%20expenses%20for%20the%20house.%20I%20had%20enough%20to%20live%20on%20with%20my%20pensions%20and%20Social%20Security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20resigned%20from%20my%20job%20and%20booked%20my%20first%20house%20sit%20that%20winter%20in%20Breckenridge%2C%20Colorado.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20children%20were%20concerned%20for%20my%20safety%20at%20first%20but%20never%20tried%20to%20dissuade%20me.%20I%20think%20they%20are%20proud%20of%20me%20for%20having%20the%20courage%20to%20do%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20first%20day%20of%20my%20retirement%20at%2059%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20after%20a%20shih%20tzu%20called%20Snowy%20in%20a%20condo%20overlooking%20the%20mountains.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20on%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20few%20issues%20finding%20the%20white-colored%20dog%20when%20he%20went%20out%20to%20play%20in%20the%20snow-covered%20backyard.%20Apart%20from%20that%2C%20it%20went%20swimmingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20choose%20a%20good%20house%20sit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20now%20completed%20over%2025%20house%20sits.%20I%20choose%20houses%20in%20destinations%20I%20want%20to%20travel%20to.%20I've%20looked%20after%20a%20miniature%20schnauzer%20in%20New%20Zealand%2C%20who%20loved%20exploring%20the%20vineyards%20with%20me%3B%20I%20have%20sat%20for%20a%20fluffy%20cat%20in%20New%20York%2C%20and%20I%20looked%20after%20four%20energetic%20dogs%20at%20a%20riverside%20home%20in%20Botswana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20owners%20interview%20me%20before%20selecting%20me%2C%20while%20others%20just%20make%20the%20booking%20through%20Trusted%20Housesitters.%20Once%20the%20sit%20is%20confirmed%2C%20the%20owners%20will%20share%20any%20other%20information%20I%20need%20by%20phone%2C%20text%20or%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20long%20house%20sits%20of%20six%20weeks%20to%20three%20months.%20When%20I%20take%20on%20a%20house%20sit%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20I'm%20close%20to%20public%20transport%20or%20have%20access%20to%20a%20car.%20I%20also%20ask%20that%20the%20owners%20leave%20a%20telephone%20number%20for%20the%20vet%20and%20a%20neighbor%20if%20I%20have%20any%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20house-sitting%20in%20Botswana%2C%20one%20of%20the%20dogs%20got%20stung%20by%20a%20hornet.%20I%20had%20to%20whisk%20him%20to%20the%20vet%20as%20he%20had%20an%20allergic%20reaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20I%20spend%20my%20days%20as%20a%20retiree%20who%20house-sits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20looking%20after%20a%20dog%2C%20I%20get%20up%20early%20to%20take%20them%20for%20a%20walk.%20If%20it's%20a%20cat%2C%20I'll%20get%20up%20and%20feed%20it%2C%20and%20then%20I%20will%20relax%20with%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20while%20researching%20what%20to%20do%20in%20the%20area.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20St%20Croix%2C%20in%20the%20US%20Virgin%20Islands%2C%20the%20house%20had%20a%20gorgeous%20pool%20overlooking%20a%20golf%20course%20and%20the%20Caribbean%20Sea.%20I%20started%20my%20day%20admiring%20the%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20something%20at%20least%20every%20other%20day.%20In%20New%20Zealand%20I%20went%20whale-watching%2C%20in%20Japan%20it%20was%20a%20cooking%20class%20.%20I%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-airbnb-experience-tour-make-money-hosts-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirbnb%20Experiences%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20also%20joined%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meetup.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeetup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20social%20platform%20that%20organizes%20in-person%20and%20virtual%20activities.%20When%20I%20go%20out%20at%20night%20as%20a%20single%20woman%20traveler%2C%20I%20like%20to%20be%20in%20a%20group.%20It's%20only%20occasionally%20I%20feel%20unsafe.%20Usually%2C%20it's%20here%20in%20the%20States%20because%20everyone%20has%20got%20guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20sold%20my%20house%20and%20bought%20a%20property%20I%20could%20rent%20on%20Airbnb%20while%20I%20travel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20initially%20rented%20my%20house%20for%20a%20year%20at%20a%20time%20in%20Denver%2C%20but%20by%202019%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20a%20more%20flexible%20solution.%20I%20needed%20somewhere%20to%20live%20in%20between%20sits.%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20hotels%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20keep%20asking%20family%20and%20friends%20to%20put%20me%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sold%20my%20house%20and%20looked%20for%20a%20home%20that%20could%20be%20a%20base%20for%20me%20and%20attract%20short-term%20renters%20on%20Airbnb.%20I%20bought%20a%20small%20townhouse%20in%20downtown%20Denver%20with%20a%20rooftop%20deck%20that%20Airbnb%20bookers%20might%20like%2C%20and%20a%20double%20garage%20I%20could%20lock%20and%20use%20as%20my%20storage%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I've%20been%20so%20busy%20with%20house%20sits%20recently%20I%20haven't%20stayed%20there%20for%20almost%20a%20year.%20I%20cover%20my%20mortgage%20and%20bills%20with%20my%20pensions%20and%20Social%20Security.%20I've%20made%20as%20much%20as%20%2477%2C000%20a%20year%20in%20bookings%20on%20Airbnb.%20The%20extra%20money%20it%20gives%20me%20means%20that%20when%20I%20need%20to%20book%20a%20long-haul%20flight%2C%20I%20can%20travel%20business%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pandemic%20made%20international%20travel%20impossible%2C%20I%20stayed%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20It%20gave%20me%20the%20chance%20to%20visit%20places%20that%20I'd%20never%20seen%20before.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20some%20downsides%20to%20housesitting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20have%20a%20limit%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20pets%20I%20sit%20for%2C%20but%20I%20think%20I%20should.%20My%20last%20house%20sit%20in%20Naples%2C%20Florida%2C%20included%20two%20dogs%2C%20two%20cats%2C%20a%20guinea%20pig%2C%20two%20geckos%2C%20and%20a%20tortoise.%20I%20had%20to%20feed%20live%20worms%20to%20the%20geckos.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20times%20when%20I'm%20lonely.%20However%2C%20I'd%20be%20more%20lonely%20at%20home%20because%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20as%20much%20motivation%20to%20go%20out%20and%20do%20things.%20When%20you're%20in%20a%20strange%20city%2C%20you%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20say%20I%20want%20to%20go%20to%20that%20museum%20or%20visit%20that%20caf%C3%A9.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20veteran%20house%20sitter%2C%20I%20get%20repeat%20bookings.%20I%20already%20have%20a%20repeat%20booking%20for%20New%20Zealand%20in%20November%202024.%20My%20housesits%20have%20now%20become%20friends%2C%20and%20we%20stay%20in%20touch.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20fabulous%20life%20as%20a%20divorced%20woman%20in%20her%20sixties%20could%20be.%20I%20can't%20believe%20this%20is%20my%20life%20and%20this%20is%20what%20I%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-house-sitter-travels-world-renting-house-aribnb-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706782541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ba7af943bb77284ba21a47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-house-sitter-travels-world-renting-house-aribnb-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Retiree%20and%20house-sitter%20Bernadine%20Swale%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20started%20traveling%20the%20world%2C%20staying%20in%20beautiful%20houses%20for%20free.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Claire%20Turrell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-house-sitter-travels-world-renting-house-aribnb-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actor%20Darshan%20Jariwala%20steps%20down%20as%20VP%20from%20CINTAA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706782533000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107324878%2Cimgsize-51286.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fexclusive-actor-darshan-jariwala-steps-down-as-vice-president-and-other-posts-from-cintaa%2Farticleshow%2F107324764.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor%20Darshan%20Jariwala%20resigns%20from%20CINTAA%20after%20a%20cheating%20complaint.%20He%20stepped%20down%20from%20all%20three%20positions%20to%20protect%20CINTAA's%20reputation.%20Jariwala's%20resignation%20aims%20to%20spare%20his%20colleagues%20from%20trouble%20and%20promises%20to%20clear%20his%20name.%20General%20Secretary%20Amit%20Behl%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSince%20it%20was%20affecting%20the%20reputation%20of%20Cintaa%20he%20has%20resigned%20from%20all%20the%20three%20positions.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Take%20Expert%20Opinion%20on%20EVMs'%20Safety%2C%20Implement%20Safeguards%3A%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20to%20Election%20Commission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09193848%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.38.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFormer%20secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20has%20written%20another%20letter%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20security%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20boards%20of%20the%20companies%20managing%20these%20machines%20are%20full%20of%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20nominees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20his%20full%20letter%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%5CnFormer%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShri%20Rajiv%20Kumar%3Cbr%3E%5CnChief%20Election%20Commissioner%3Cbr%3E%5CnElection%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShri%20A%20C%20Pandey%3Cbr%3E%5CnElection%20Commissioner%3Cbr%3E%5CnElection%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShri%20Arun%20Goel%3Cbr%3E%5CnElection%20Commissioner%3Cbr%3E%5CnElection%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDear%20S%2FShri%20Rajiv%20Kumar%2F%20Pandey%2F%20Goel%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20refer%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneylife.in%2Farticle%2Fcan-bjps-office-bearers-run-the-affairs-of-bharat-electronics-which-makes-evms-asks-eas-sarma%2F73235.html%5C%22%3Emy%20letter%20of%20January%2026%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20the%20BJP%20has%20loaded%20the%20Boards%20of%20both%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Ltd%20(BEL)%20and%20the%20Electronics%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Ltd%20(ECIL)%20with%20its%20nominees%20and%20how%20it%20has%20cast%20a%20shadow%20on%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20use%20of%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20manufactured%20and%20supplied%20by%20those%20two%20CPSEs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2023%2F03%2Felection-commission-of-india-must-question-the-presence-political-nominees-on-bels-and-ecils-boards%2F%5C%22%3Ecautioned%20the%20Commission%20as%20early%20as%2023-3-2023%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20this%20and%2C%20once%20again%2C%20reminded%20it%20on%2026-1-2024%2C%20I%20find%20that%20the%20Commission%20has%20failed%20to%20invoke%20its%20authority%20under%20Article%20324%20and%20direct%20the%20Government%20to%20withdraw%20the%20BJP%20nominees%20from%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20and%20ECIL%E2%80%99s%20Boards.%20The%20Commission%20is%20either%20insensitive%20to%20the%20conflict%20of%20interest%20that%20is%20explicitly%20evident%20or%20is%20reluctant%20to%20displease%20the%20political%20executive%2C%20which%20in%20my%20view%20amounts%20to%20allowing%20the%20ruling%20political%20party%20brazenly%20to%20tilt%20the%20level%20playing%20ground%20among%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20the%20public%20interest.%20How%20can%20the%20Commission%20discharge%20its%20Constitutional%20responsibility%20of%20conducting%20elections%20in%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20manner%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20have%20pointed%20out%20time%20and%20again%2C%20EVM%20technology%20as%20it%20is%20the%20case%20today%20is%20not%20only%20vulnerable%20to%20manipulation%20but%20also%20violates%20the%20secrecy%20of%20voting%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20its%20inability%20to%20permit%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmixing%E2%80%9D%20of%20booth-wise%20ballots%20within%20a%20constituency%2C%20since%20it%20does%20not%20use%20totalisers.%20In%20my%20view%2C%20this%20is%20a%20serious%20legal%20infringement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20EVMs%20to%20manipulation%20is%20concerned%2C%20I%20invite%20your%20attention%20to%20the%20expert%20opinion%20offered%20by%20Madhav%20Deshpande%2C%20a%20professional%20who%20has%20studied%20the%20EVM%20system%20in%20depth%2C%20when%20he%20appeared%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz5Y6z29El3I%5C%22%3Evideo%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20would%20earnestly%20advise%20the%20Commission%20to%20invite%20Madhav%20Deshpande%20to%20appreciate%20his%20concerns%20and%20to%20adopt%20the%20remedial%20measures%20suggested%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBriefly%2C%20the%20EVM%20system%20consists%20of%20a%20Ballot%20unit%2C%20a%20VVPAT%20unit%20and%20a%20Control%20unit.%20Since%20the%20system%20is%20a%20stand-alone%20one%2C%20it%20may%20be%20difficult%20to%20%E2%80%9Chack%E2%80%9D%20it.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20Ballot%20unit%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20Control%20unit%20via%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%2C%20the%20voter%20is%20never%20sure%20whether%20the%20vote%20cast%20by%20him%2Fher%20has%20been%20correctly%20conveyed%20by%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20to%20the%20Control%20Unit%20which%20determines%20the%20final%20vote%20count.%20If%20the%20sequencing%20of%20these%20units%20is%20changed%20such%20that%20the%20Ballot%20Unit%20conveys%20the%20vote%20simultaneously%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20and%20Control%20units%20where%20the%20electronically%20transmitted%20vote%20is%20to%20be%20registered%20and%20counted%2C%20this%20issue%20could%20be%20resolved%20to%20some%20extent.%20If%20it%20is%20not%20changed%20thus%2C%20there%20is%20no%20certainty%20that%20the%20vote%20cast%20through%20the%20Ballot%20unit%20is%20correctly%20conveyed%20by%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20to%20the%20Control%20Unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Ballot%20unit%20and%20the%20Control%20unit%20are%20randomised%20and%20therefore%20independent%20of%20the%20location%20wherever%20they%20are%20used%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20is%20location-specific%2C%20as%20constituency-wise%2C%20candidate-wise%20information%20is%20uploaded%20into%20it%20a%20few%20days%20before%20it%20is%20deployed.%20To%20that%20extent%2C%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20data%20fed%20into%20it%20and%20the%20format%20in%20which%20it%20is%20fed.%20Though%20only%20authorised%20persons%20are%20allowed%20to%20attend%20to%20this%2C%20since%20it%20is%20a%20manual%20operation%2C%20even%20without%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20authorised%20persons%2C%20the%20format%20in%20which%20the%20data%20is%20uploaded%20into%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20may%20leave%20room%20for%20manipulation.%20Such%20manipulation%20may%20result%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20conveying%20the%20vote%20cast%20in%20favour%20of%20one%20candidate%20to%20another%20candidate%20unless%20the%20process%20of%20feeding%20the%20data%20module%20into%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20is%20subject%20to%20independent%20expert%20oversight%20and%20surveillance%20by%20all%20political%20parties.%20The%20absence%20of%20such%20independent%20surveillance%20makes%20the%20system%20vulnerable%20to%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mere%20100%25%20cross-verification%20of%20the%20electronic%20votes%20counted%20vis-a-vis%20the%20VVPAT%20count%20may%20not%20fully%20address%20this%20issue.%20It%20calls%20for%20a%20far%20more%20verification%20process%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20explained%20by%20Madhav%20Deshpande%2C%20the%20next%20possibility%20of%20manipulation%20arises%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpairing%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20units%20with%20the%20corresponding%20Control%20units%20through%20a%20connecting%20cable%20and%20a%20secure%20unique%20electronic%20key%20so%20that%20once%20a%20Control%20unit%20registers%20the%20votes%20cast%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20replaced%20by%20another%20one%20to%20manipulate%20the%20vote%20count.%20If%20a%20Control%20unit%20is%20replaced%20after%20votes%20are%20registered%20but%20before%20counting%20starts%2C%20if%20the%20VVPAT%20and%20Control%20units%20are%20electronically%20%E2%80%9Cpaired%E2%80%9D%20and%20can%20recognise%20each%20other%2C%20it%20will%20not%20allow%20the%20newly%20introduced%20Control%20unit%20to%20recognise%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20which%20has%20registered%20the%20votes.%20At%20present%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20such%20a%20serial%20connection%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20electronically%20secured%20%E2%80%9Cpairing%E2%80%9D%2C%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20possibility%20of%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20in%20the%20present%20arrangement%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20track%20a%20Control%20unit%20once%20votes%20are%20registered%20by%20it.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20traceability%20of%20a%20Control%20unit%20which%20has%20registered%20the%20votes%20cast%2C%20so%20that%20those%20who%20undertake%20counting%20or%20those%20overseeing%20it%20may%20readily%20know%20if%20it%20is%20moved%20to%20a%20different%20location%20unauthorisedly%20to%20permit%20manipulation.%20To%20permit%20traceability%2C%20the%20Control%20Unit%20needs%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cgeo-tagged%E2%80%9D%20without%20the%20necessity%20of%20the%20Control%20unit%20itself%20being%20connected%20to%20the%20internet.%20The%20geo-tag%20can%20be%20sealed%20so%20that%20no%20one%20may%20tamper%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Madhav%20Deshpande%20has%20so%20clearly%20explained%20calls%20for%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20A%20rearrangement%20of%20the%20configuration%20such%20that%20the%20Ballot%20Unit%20may%20convey%20information%20on%20votes%20cast%20simultaneously%20to%20the%20Control%20Unit%20and%20the%20VVPAT%20Unit%20directly%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20Subject%20uploading%20of%20Constituency-wise%2C%20and%20candidate-wise%20data%20and%20its%20format%20into%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20to%20an%20independent%20technical%20audit%20under%20scrutiny%20by%20all%20political%20parties%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20Ensure%20%E2%80%9Cpairing%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20and%20Control%20Units%20before%20they%20are%20connected%20for%20voting%20through%20a%20secure%20unique%20electronic%20coupling%20arrangement%20and%20subject%20that%20process%20to%20scrutiny%20by%20all%20political%20parties%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4.%20Geo-tag%20each%20Control%20unit%20under%20a%20seal%20to%20prevent%20their%20unauthorised%20movement%2C%20once%20again%20subject%20to%20independent%20technical%20audit%20and%20scrutiny%20by%20all%20political%20parties%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20measures%20are%20urgently%20called%20for%20and%20I%20hope%20that%20the%20Commission%20will%20implement%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20suggest%20that%20the%20Commission%20invite%20Madhav%20Deshpande%20to%20explain%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgaps%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Choles%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20EVM%20system%20pointed%20out%20by%20him%20and%20additional%20remedial%20measures%20to%20be%20taken%20so%20that%20the%20Commission%20may%20take%20such%20urgent%20measures%20as%20necessary%20to%20dispel%20the%20public%20concerns%20about%20the%20use%20of%20EVMs%20and%20elicit%20public%20trust%20in%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%2C%20the%20independence%20of%20which%20has%20come%20under%20judicial%20scrutiny%2C%20cannot%20afford%20to%20function%20in%20secrecy.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20Commission%20has%20shown%20reluctance%20to%20meet%20a%20delegation%20of%20opposition%20leaders%20on%20their%20EVM%20concerns%20has%20further%20reinforced%20the%20growing%20doubts%20about%20its%20independence.%20The%20Commission%20cannot%20afford%20to%20deify%20the%20existing%20EVM%20technology%20and%20obstinately%20defend%20it%20without%20reason%20or%20rhyme.%20I%20may%20remind%20the%20Commission%20that%20it%20is%20funded%20by%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%2C%20not%20by%20the%20ruling%20political%20executive%20and%20it%20cannot%20afford%20to%20shy%20away%20from%20public%20accountability.%20Nor%20can%20it%20abandon%20the%20obligation%20cast%20on%20it%20by%20Article%20324%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20be%20independent%20enough%20to%20conduct%20elections%20in%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20ruling%20political%20executive%20has%20chosen%20to%20ignore%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20suggestion%20to%20have%20an%20independent%20process%20for%20selecting%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Commission%20has%20displayed%20unwillingness%20time%20and%20again%20to%20penalise%20senior%20political%20leaders%20occupying%20high%20public%20offices%20for%20violating%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20(MCC)%20gives%20one%20the%20impression%20that%20is%20unwilling%20to%20function%20independent%20of%20the%20political%20executive%20and%20safeguard%20the%20public%20interest.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20Commission%20has%20not%20chosen%20to%20direct%20the%20government%20to%20revamp%20the%20Boards%20of%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20to%20exclude%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20representatives%20from%20their%20respective%20Boards%20leads%20one%20to%20the%20inevitable%20inference%20that%20the%20line%20between%20the%20political%20executive%20and%20the%20Commission%20is%20getting%20totally%20blurred.%20This%20situation%20does%20not%20augur%20well%20for%20the%20future%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20unless%20the%20Commission%20wakes%20up%20and%20corrects%20it%20urgently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20that%20you%20will%20take%20this%20seriously%2C%20plug%20the%20%E2%80%9Choles%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cgaps%E2%80%9D%20pointed%20out%20by%20Madhav%20Deshpande%20immediately%20and%20start%20functioning%20independently%20and%20transparently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegards%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYours%20sincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%5CnVisakhapatnam%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1-2-2024%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706782521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09193848%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.38.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftake-expert-opinion-on-evms-safety-implement-safeguards-e-a-s-sarma-to-election-commission%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEVM%20technology%20as%20it%20is%20the%20case%20today%20is%20not%20only%20vulnerable%20to%20manipulation%20but%20also%20violates%20the%20secrecy%20of%20voting%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20its%20inability%20to%20p