kTok%2C%20women%20who%20have%20adopted%20the%20stay-at-home%20girlfriend%20label%20often%20rack%20up%20millions%20of%20views%20on%20their%20day-in-the-life%20videos%2C%20in%20which%20they%20make%20breakfast%20for%20their%20partners%2C%20tidy%20their%20homes%2C%20go%20for%20leisurely%20walks%2C%20and%20lounge%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20never%20clocking%20in%20for%20a%209-to-5%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lifestyle%20appeals%20to%20women%20who%20feel%20overwhelmed%20and%20overworked%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhustle-culture-got-america-addicted-to-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehustle%20culture%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20some%20people%20commenting%20on%20social%20media%20posts%20say%20that%20the%20trend%20glamorizes%20unhealthy%20financial%20dependence%20and%20gender%20inequality%2C%20BI%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Williams%2C%20it's%20a%20common%20misconception%20that%20receiving%20financial%20help%20from%20her%20partner%20means%20that%20she's%20giving%20up%20her%20self-autonomy.%20In%20contrast%2C%20she%20said%20that%20allowing%20her%20boyfriend%20to%20take%20care%20of%20certain%20aspects%20of%20her%20life%20has%20been%20a%20practice%20in%20letting%20go%20of%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fattachment-theory-author-says-we-need-more-empathy-for-avoidants-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextreme%20self-reliance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20internal%20struggle%20that%20she's%20still%20overcoming.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20this%2C%20I%20was%20in%20survival%20mode%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20I%20was%20going%20to%20keep%20a%20roof%20over%20my%20head.%20Now%20I%20can%20completely%20focus%20on%20my%20health%20and%20lean%20into%20building%20my%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20embracing%20the%20stay-at-home%20girlfriend%20lifestyle%20has%20empowered%20her%20to%20live%20with%20less%20stress%20and%20more%20time%20for%20her%20passions%20and%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20become%20a%20stay-at-home-girlfriend%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Williams%20chatted%20with%20Dre%20for%20the%20first%20time%20at%20a%20church-run%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-invented-chaotic-singles-party-after-dating-app-frustration-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingles%20night%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%202023%2C%20she%20learned%20that%20he%20was%20seeking%20a%20life%20partner%20to%20marry%20and%20support%20emotionally%2C%20spiritually%20%E2%80%94%20and%20financially.%20At%20first%2C%20Williams%20said%20she%20was%20skeptical.%20But%20a%20few%20months%20into%20their%20relationship%2C%20when%20Williams%20felt%20ashamed%20to%20ask%20Dre%20to%20lend%20her%20money%20for%20groceries%20that%20she%20couldn't%20afford%20at%20the%20time%2C%20she%20realized%20her%20dream%20of%20becoming%20a%20stay-at-home%20partner%20could%20be%20a%20reality%20that%20made%20sense%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20me%20that%20I%20could%20come%20to%20him%20for%20those%20things%20and%20that%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20feel%20bad%20asking%20for%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20told%20BI.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShe%20had%20no%20prior%20experience%20as%20a%20stay-at-home%20girlfriend%2C%20but%20the%20lifestyle%20was%20one%20she%20saw%20modeled%20in%20her%20family%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222865%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stella%20Williams%2C%20a%20content%20creator%2C%20cuddles%20up%20to%20her%20boyfriend.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ba795843bb77284ba2186f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222149%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWilliams%20met%20her%20boyfriend%20Dre%20through%20a%20church%20event%2C%20and%20quickly%20learned%20that%20he%20had%20similar%20values%20to%20her%2C%20she%20said.%3Cp%3EStella%20Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20Latina%2C%20and%20I've%20always%20seen%20that%20the%20women%20are%20well%20taken%20care%20of.%20They're%20having%20your%20children%20and%20they're%20the%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20had%20low%20self-esteem%20and%20didn't%20feel%20good%20enough%20for%20that%20lifestyle.%20I%20settled%20for%20less%20until%20I%20met%20my%20current%20partner%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20a%20stay-at-home%20girlfriend%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20and%20her%20partner%20often%20joke%20that%20%26quot%3BMy%20money%20is%20my%20money%2C%20and%20his%20money%20is%20our%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20In%20their%20day-to-day%20lives%2C%20the%20quip%20holds%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20mornings%2C%20Williams%20and%20Dre%20wake%20up%20at%205%3A45%20a.m.%20to%20eat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fhealthy-breakfast-ideas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreakfast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20typically%20toast%20with%20cream%20cheese%20and%20jam%20and%20homemade%20lattes%20that%20Williams%20whips%20up%20for%20both%20of%20them.%20For%20the%20next%20hour%2C%20they%20participate%20in%20an%20online%20prayer%20group%20before%20Dre%20gets%20ready%20for%20work%20and%20Williams%20plans%20out%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20day%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20she'll%20dive%20into%20work%20for%20her%20social%20media%20pages.%20Right%20now%2C%20she's%20pivoting%20her%20brand%20to%20focus%20on%20travel%20content%2C%20so%20she%20researches%20destinations%20and%20brainstorms%20ideas%2C%20she%20said.%20Any%20money%20that%20comes%20from%20her%20work%20is%20solely%20hers%20and%20she%20uses%20it%20to%20pay%20for%20work-related%20bills%20like%20new%20filming%20equipment%2C%20Williams%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20noon%2C%20Williams%20stops%20working%20and%20goes%20to%20a%20pilates%2C%20barre%2C%20or%20yoga%20class%20that%