0manager%20of%20McDonough%20Investments%20highlighted%20Buffett's%20comments%20about%20Pilot's%20real%20estate%20during%20Berkshire's%20annual%20meeting%20last%20year.%20The%20Berkshire%20CEO%20described%20its%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20hundreds%20of%20locations%20on%20the%20interstate%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20nothing%20like%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20going%20to%20move%20the%20interstate%20two%20miles%20to%20the%20right%20or%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20probably%20continue%20traveling%20on%20highways%20for%20many%20decades%2C%20and%20Pilot%20should%20be%20in%20some%20good%20locations%20to%20serve%20those%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20McDonough%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20durable%20advantage%20that%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20ruin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20to%20Pilot's%20strong%20brand%20and%20the%20consistent%20quality%20of%20experience%20it%20provides%20compared%20to%20other%20truck%20stops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20is%20famous%20for%20prizing%20assets%20%26quot%3Bmoats%26quot%3B%20or%20durable%20barriers%20to%20competition%20like%20brands%20and%20real%20estate%2C%20so%20it's%20likely%20he%20bought%20Pilot%20in%20part%20because%20of%20its%20strengths%20on%20that%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathway-turnaround-story-mcdonough-pilot-real-estate-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706780554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3aa90de89ebf001f04541d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathway-turnaround-story-mcdonough-pilot-real-estate-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Warren%20Buffett's%20company%20beat%20the%20odds%20given%20its%20original%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Btextiles%2C%20tr