ot-2024-02-01-at-1.41.56-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20national%20flag%2C%20the%20Tricolour%2C%20was%20fluttering%20atop%20a%20newly%20constructed%20108-feet%20flag%20post%20in%20Keragodu%20village%20of%20Mandya%20when%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0visited%20on%20Monday%2C%2029%20January.%20The%20shiny%20new%20high-mast%20flagpole%20is%20visible%20from%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20feet%20below%20the%20Tricolour%2C%20a%20photo%20of%20Hindu%20god%20Rama%20and%20a%20triangular%20saffron%20flag%20on%20a%20wooden%20stick%20is%20tied%2C%20as%20if%20in%20a%20mark%20of%20protest%2C%20to%20the%20flagpole%20that%20is%20now%20surrounded%20by%20police%20barricades.%20Villagers%20had%20shut%20down%20businesses%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvoluntary%20bandh%E2%80%9D%20on%20Monday%2C%20protesting%20against%20police%20for%20replacing%20the%20saffron%20flag%20with%20the%20national%20flag%20a%20day%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flag%20post%2C%20contradictory%20to%20claims%2C%20is%20not%20on%20temple%20land%20but%20across%20the%20road%20from%20an%20old%20Hanuman%20temple.%20The%20land%20belongs%20to%20the%20government%20but%20the%20flag%20post%2C%20the%20villagers%20proudly%20claim%2C%20was%20built%20using%20funds%20they%20pooled%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20week%2C%20this%20flag%20post%20has%20been%20used%20to%20hoist%20a%20saffron%20flag%20with%20Hanuman%E2%80%99s%20image%20and%20the%20Indian%20national%20flag%2C%20alternatively%2C%20several%20times.%20While%20everyone%20knows%20who%20hoisted%20the%20national%20flag%2C%20nobody%20seems%20to%20know%20who%20hoisted%20the%20saffron%20flag%20with%20a%20religious%20chant%20of%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%2C%20especially%20since%20it%20was%20hoisted%20in%20violation%20of%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20flagpole%20that%20has%20unfurled%20polarisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20newly%20installed%20high-mast%20flagpole%20in%20Keragodu%20of%20Mandya%20district%20has%20turned%20into%20the%20epicentre%20of%20communal%20turmoil%2C%20just%20in%20time%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%202024.%20This%20village%20is%20now%20divided%20between%20a%20saffron%20flag%20and%20the%20national%20flag.%20A%20visit%20to%20the%20village%20reveals%20a%20tale%20of%20mobilisation%20for%20the%20assertion%20of%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20identity%E2%80%9D%2C%20subversion%20of%20mandate%20to%20break%20rules%20and%20eventual%20outburst%20of%20public%20outcry%20against%20the%20administration%20aided%20by%20half-truths%20and%20polarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaffron%20(Kesari)%20bunts%20adorned%20the%20Mandya-Gubbi%20Main%20Road%2C%20featuring%20flags%20depicting%20Lord%20Rama%20and%20Hanuman.%20These%20vibrant%20displays%20lined%20the%20main%20road%2C%20creating%20an%20unmissable%20welcome%20for%20commuters%20passing%20through%20Keragodu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20boasts%20of%20three%20heritage%20temples%3A%20The%20main%20Anjaneya%20(Hanuman)%20temple%2C%20the%20Basaveshwara%20temple%2C%20and%20the%20Vigneshwara%20temple.%20The%20latter%20two%20temples%20stand%20100%20feet%20apart%20on%20opposite%20sides%20of%20the%20road.%20The%20Gowrishankar%20Trust%20has%20been%20actively%20conducting%20religious%20programmes%20relating%20to%20all%20three%20deities%20of%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flagpole%20in%20Keragodu%2C%20featuring%20a%20motorised%20flag%20%E2%80%98hoister%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98lowerer%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20sight%20to%20behold%20for%20the%20locals.%20Trust%20member%20Byre%20Gowda%20told%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20has%20to%20attach%20the%20flag%20to%20a%20frame%20and%20just%20press%20a%20switch%2C%20and%20the%20flag%20gets%20hoisted.%20There%20is%20another%20switch%20to%20lower%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Trust%20associate%20Shankare%20Gowda%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20flagpole%20was%20funded%20entirely%20by%20the%20villagers%2C%20who%20collected%20a%20total%20of%20%E2%82%B93.6%20lakh%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20daily-wage%20labourers%20contributed%20whatever%20they%20could%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20There%20was%20absolutely%20no%20help%2C%20financially%2C%20from%20the%20village%20panchayat%20or%20the%20government%20for%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20flagpole.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPermission%20sought%2C%20granted%2C%20and%20violated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20high-mast%20flagpole%2C%20there%20used%20to%20be%20a%20smaller%20iron%20flagpole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangala%20Gowramma%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Keragodu%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20would%20be%20frequent%20bhajans%20and%20pujas%20at%20the%20Anjaneya%20temple%20on%20Saturdays%20and%20we%20used%20to%20hoist%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20on%20that%20small%20flagpole%20during%20Hanuma%20Jayanthi.%20We%20associate%20ourselves%20very%20closely%20with%20the%20Anjaneya%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20centuries%20old%20in%20Keragodu.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGowramma%20was%20just%20returning%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Epadayatra%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20protest%20towards%20the%20District%20Collector%E2%80%99s%20office.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20not%20even%20a%20single%20Ram%20temple%20in%20the%20entire%20Keragodu%20village.%20There%20is%20only%20this%20auspicious%20Anjaneya%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20favourite.%20We%20have%20been%20observing%20and%20celebrating%20all%20Hanuman%20festivities%20for%20the%20past%2040%20years.%20As%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20was%20being%20built%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20we%20thought%20that%20we%20would%20conduct%20a%2048-day%20ritual%20starting%20from%2022%20January%20%E2%80%94%20the%20day%20of%20its%20consecration%20%E2%80%94%20and%20continue%20with%20bhajans%20and%20pujas%20at%20the%20Anjaneya%20temple%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20permission%20obtained%20from%20the%20village%20Mandal%20Panchayat%20for%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%2C%20Gowramma%20said%20that%20authorities%20unexpectedly%20replaced%20it%20with%20the%20Tricolour%20after%20Republic%20Day%2C%20leading%20to%20accusations%20of%20disrespecting%20the%20national%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20observe%20two%20national%20holidays%20%E2%80%94%20Independence%20Day%20and%20Republic%20Day%20%E2%80%94%20by%20hoisting%20the%20Tricolour%2C%20and%20also%20Karnataka%20Rajyotsava%20by%20hoisting%20the%20Karnataka%20flag.%20We%20hoist%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20during%20some%20occasions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGowramma%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20hoisting%20the%20flag%20at%203%20pm%20and%20the%20failure%20to%20lower%20it%20after%20sunset%2C%20deeming%20it%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20national%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20hoisted%20the%20saffron%20flag%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Keragodu%20Mandal%20Panchayat%20President%20Naveen%20Kumar%20TS%20told%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20new%20flagpole%20was%20installed%20by%20Gowrishankar%20Trust%20members%20and%20villagers%2C%20and%20was%20inaugurated%20on%20the%20evening%20of%2020%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trust%20sought%20permission%20from%20the%20panchayat%20on%2029%20December%2C%202023%2C%20after%20giving%20a%20written%20undertaking%20that%20they%20would%20hoist%20only%20the%20national%20and%20state%20flag%20on%20the%20newly-installed%20flagpole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20undertaking%20dated%2017%20January%2C%20signed%20by%20seven%20members%20of%20the%20Gowrishankar%20Trust%2C%20assuring%20that%20no%20norms%20will%20be%20violated%20and%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20ensuring%20no%20unsavoury%20incidents%20take%20place%2C%20is%20also%20with%20the%20panchayat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%E2%80%9Csomeone%E2%80%9D%20hoisted%20a%20Hanuman%20flag%20on%20the%20same%20night%20of%20the%20inauguration%20against%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20was%20already%20hoisted%20and%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20consecration%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20the%20next%20day%20(22%20January)%2C%20we%20did%20not%20want%20to%20rake%20up%20any%20controversy%20and%20immediately%20called%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98Santhane%20Sabhe%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mediation%20meeting%20with%20all%20the%20Gram%20Panchayat%20members%20and%20the%20villagers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20villagers%20wanted%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20to%20remain%20hoisted%20at%20that%20time%2C%20and%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20panchayat%20members%20objected%20to%20it%2C%20stating%20that%20if%20the%20panchayat%20gives%20permission%20for%20a%20religious%20flag%20this%20time%2C%20then%20other%20religious%20organisations%20might%20approach%20and%20seek%20permission%20to%20hoist%20their%20flag%20during%20some%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20politics%20of%20a%20flagpole%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Panchayat%20member%2C%20KL%20Krishna%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20village%20of%20Keragodu%20is%20a%20JD(S)-dominated%20area.%C2%A0It%20was%20evident%20from%20the%20buzzing%20junction%20with%20tall%20hoardings%20and%20banners%20of%20JD(S)%20leader%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20his%20son%20Nikhil%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20along%20with%20local%20party%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20group%20of%20JD(S)%20and%20BJP%20workers%2C%20joined%20by%20Bajrang%20Dal%20activists%2C%20went%20around%20the%20village%20and%20collected%20around%201%2C000%20petitions%20demanding%20that%20the%20panchayat%20grant%20permission%20for%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20to%20be%20left%20hoisted%20until%20such%20time%20that%20the%20Anjaneya%20rituals%20are%20concluded%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%20spotted%20a%20few%20Congress%20youth%20workers%20who%20had%20come%20wearing%20saffron%20shawls.%20They%20asserted%20that%20they%20were%20for%20Hindutva%20and%20hence%2C%20their%20presence%20there.%20They%20noted%20that%20though%20it%20is%20a%20JD(S)-dominated%20area%2C%20it%20looked%20like%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20workers%20had%20already%20hijacked%20the%20JD(S)%E2%80%99%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20petitions%20reached%20the%20village%20panchayat%2C%20they%20called%20for%20a%20general%20Gram%20Sabha%20meeting%20on%2025%20January%20between%20the%20villagers%2C%20comprising%20mostly%20of%20the%20Gowrishankar%20Trust%20members%2C%20and%20the%20opposing%20panchayat%20members%20who%20wanted%20to%20follow%20the%20norms%20and%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panchayat%20decided%20that%20the%20villagers%20would%20observe%20%E2%80%9Cstatus%20quo%E2%80%9D%20until%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20meeting%20as%20it%20was%20Republic%20Day%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panchayat%20members%20finally%20drew%20up%20the%20violations%20committed%20by%20the%20trust%20members%20for%20having%20hoisted%20a%20religious%20flag%20without%20permission.%20They%20immediately%20annulled%20the%20permission%20granted%20to%20the%20trust%20and%20directed%20them%20to%20lower%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20and%20hoist%20the%20national%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20continued%20to%20soar%20in%20the%20Keragodu%20skies%20and%20panchayat%20president%20Naveen%20Kumar%20maintained%20that%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20lower%20the%20religious%20flag%20%E2%80%94%20fearing%20for%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20subsequently%2C%20brought%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20higher%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20Executive%20Officer%20(EO)%2C%20the%20Panchayat%20Development%20Officer%20(PDO)%2C%20and%20the%20Taluk%20Panchayat%20Officer%20(TPO)%2C%20who%20granted%20Kumar%20three%20days%E2%80%99%20time%20to%20set%20right%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20Republic%20Day%2C%20the%20Gowrishankar%20Trust%20members%2C%20associates%2C%20and%20a%20few%20villagers%20brought%20down%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20and%20hoisted%20the%20Tricolour%20with%20a%20decorated%20photograph%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20placed%20beneath%20the%20flagpole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20the%20same%20evening%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20trust%20lowered%20the%20Tricolour%20and%20again%20hoisted%20the%20Hanuman%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20panchayat%20president%2C%20who%20inquired%20with%20the%20Gowrishankar%20Trust%20regarding%20who%20hoisted%20the%20Hanuman%20flag.%20The%20trust%20members%20maintained%20that%20they%20did%20not%20know%20who%20was%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20drama%20that%20followed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Gowrishankar%20Trust%20members%20and%20associates%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20installation%20of%20the%20high-mast%20pole%20in%20the%20village%2C%20they%20told%20authorities%20that%20they%20did%20not%20know%20who%20hoisted%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20on%20the%20evening%20of%2020%20January%20and%20again%20on%20the%20evening%20of%2026%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGram%20Panchayat%20President%20Naveen%20Kumar%20brought%20this%20matter%20to%20the%20knowledge%20of%20his%20EO%2C%20along%20with%20other%20panchayat%20officials%20from%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20and%20also%20informed%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SP)%20about%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%2027%20January%2C%20all%20the%20panchayat%20officials%20from%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20along%20with%20police%20security%20personnel%2C%20visited%20the%20flagpole%20spot%20and%20conducted%20discussions%20with%20the%20Gowrishankar%20Trust%20members%2C%20associates%2C%20villagers%2C%20and%20the%20panchayat%20members%20headed%20by%20Naveen%20Kumar.%20The%20authorities%20explained%20to%20the%20villagers%20that%20the%20norms%20of%20the%20panchayat%20should%20not%20be%20violated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20by%20then%2C%20messages%20had%20spread%20on%20WhatsApp%20that%20authorities%20had%20come%20to%20take%20down%20the%20Hanuman%20flag.%20A%20huge%20crowd%20gathered%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20panchayat%20officials.%20Since%20it%20was%20a%20sensitive%20matter%2C%20the%20officials%20attempted%20to%20explain%20to%20the%20villagers%20about%20the%20permissions%20and%20the%20norms%20of%20such%20a%20flagpole%20being%20installed%20on%20public%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20villagers%2C%20by%20then%2C%20were%20joined%20by%20hundreds%20of%20others%20from%20surrounding%20areas%20such%20as%20Pandavapura%2C%20Basaraalu%2C%20Besagarahalli%2C%20Maddur%2C%20Mallavalli%2C%20Allegere%2C%20and%20Bilidhegalu%20at%20Keragodu%20mobilised%20by%20WhatsApp%20messages.%20Since%20the%20crowd%20grew%20exponentially%2C%20the%20authorities%20chose%20not%20to%20lower%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20on%20Saturday%20but%20informed%20them%20that%20the%20Tricolour%20would%20be%20hoisted%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20around%2010.30%20am%2C%20around%20eight%20battalions%20of%20Karnataka%20State%20Reserve%20Police%20(KSRP)%20%E2%80%94%20headed%20by%20a%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20rank%20officer%20%E2%80%94%20were%20deployed%20for%20maintaining%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20village.%20The%20district%20administration%20officials%20arrived%20at%20the%20flagpole%20to%20lower%20the%20religious%20flag%20and%20hoist%20the%20Tricolour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20once%20again%20opposed%20by%20villagers%2C%20who%20this%20time%20resisted%20along%20with%20a%20large%20number%20of%20women%20folk%20from%20the%20village%20and%20surroundings%20areas%20in%20the%20front%20of%20the%20flagpole.%20Allegations%20of%20administration%20and%20government%20being%20%E2%80%9Canti-Hindu%E2%80%9D%20flew%20thick%20and%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20villagers%20refused%20to%20move%20away%2C%20the%20police%20resorted%20to%20lathi-charge%2C%20and%20the%20protesting%20women%20were%20taken%20into%20preventive%20custody.%20Three%20people%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20lathi-charge%20and%20they%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20administered%20first-aid%2C%20and%20sent%20home.%20The%20authorities%20lowered%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%2C%20hoisted%20the%20Tricolour%2C%20and%20barricaded%20the%20flagpole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20further%20imposed%20Section%20144%20(curfew)%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20after%20this%20incident%20that%20BJP%20leaders%20like%20Ashwath%20Narayan%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Legislative%20Assembly%20R%20Ashoka%2C%20and%20others%20visited%20the%20village%20and%20inquired%20into%20the%20matter.%20Ashoka%20slammed%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20for%20its%20%E2%80%9Canti-Hindu%E2%80%9D%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20fiery%20protest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20response%20to%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20and%20the%20highhandedness%20of%20the%20police%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20thousands%20of%20villagers%20were%20mobilised%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20who%20gathered%20initially%20at%20the%20Kaalikamba%20temple%20off%20the%20old%20Mandya-Mysuru%20highway%2C%20which%20is%20around%205%20km%20from%20the%20Mandya%20District%20Collector%E2%80%99s%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20trucks%20loaded%20with%20high-decibel%20speakers%20and%20generator%20sets%2C%20and%20smaller%20vehicles%20following%20these%20trucks%2C%20distributing%20water%20bottles%20to%20the%20people%20who%20were%20participating%20in%20the%20padayatra%20to%20the%20DC%E2%80%99s%20office.%20It%20was%20a%20display%20of%20brash%20religious%20fervour%20with%20saffron%20flags%20bearing%20both%20Lord%20Rama%E2%80%99s%20and%20Hanuman%E2%80%99s%20pictures%2C%20songs%20of%20Bajrang%20Dal%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rather%20rare%20sight%20in%20Vokkaliga-dominated%20Mandya%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Bajrang%20Dal%E2%80%99s%20music%20blaring%20and%20the%20crowd%20going%20berserk%20while%20dancing%20on%20the%20road%2C%20it%20was%20a%20spectacle%20for%20the%20general%20public%2C%20who%20were%20clearly%20entertained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20Hanuman%20flags%20were%20distributed%20by%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20protest%20to%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20they%20reached%20the%20Mandya%20DC%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20the%20entire%20government%20office%20was%20dotted%20with%20saffron%20flags.%20Leaders%20heading%20the%20rally%20continued%20with%20their%20speeches%20after%20which%20a%20memorandum%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20to%20allow%20the%20villagers%20to%20hoist%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20on%20the%20flagpole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20government%20was%20attempting%20to%20incite%20communal%20violence%20by%20lowering%20the%20Hanuman%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELocal%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20way%20ti%20the%20DC%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20the%20rally%20briefly%20stopped%20at%20a%20junction%20where%20hoardings%20and%20banners%20of%20Congress%20MLA%20Ravikumar%20Gowda%20alias%20Ganiga%20Ravi%20were%20put%20up.%20He%20won%20the%20last%20Assembly%20elections%20by%20a%20thin%20margin%20of%202%2C019%20votes%20against%20the%20JD(S)%20candidate%20BR%20Ramachandra%20who%20contested%20from%20the%20Mandya%20Assembly%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20started%20pelting%20stones%2C%20water%20bottles%2C%20and%20slippers%20at%20his%20banners.%20The%20police%20immediately%20resorted%20to%20lathi-charge%20and%20took%20control%20of%20the%20situation.%20They%20insisted%20that%20the%20rally%20keep%20on%20moving.%20Banners%20and%20hoardings%20placed%20along%20the%20entire%20stretch%20of%20highway%20running%20through%20Mandya%20town%20were%20torn%20and%20even%20set%20ablaze%20by%20agitators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20youth%20activists%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20who%20spoke%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20flagpole%20was%20built%20by%20a%20group%20of%20Trust%20members%20in%20Keragodu%20who%20are%20loyal%20to%20former%20prime%20minister%20and%20JD(S)%20leader%20Deva%20Gowda%2C%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20JD(S)%20contestant%20Ramachandra%20had%20lost%20the%20recent%20elections%20by%20a%20thin%20margin%20against%20Ganiga%20Ravi%2C%20the%20latter%20was%20not%20invited%20for%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20newly-constructed%20flagpole.%20They%20claimed%20that%2C%20for%20this%20reason%2C%20Ganiga%20Ravi%20settled%20scores%20by%20having%20the%20district%20administration%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMandya%20SP%20N%20Yathish%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0that%20there%20are%20a%20total%20of%20three%20cases%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20flagpole%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20under%20Section%20353%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20deter%20public%20servant%20from%20discharge%20of%20his%20duty)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20against%20the%20villagers%20in%20Keragodu%20on%2028%20January.%20On%2029%20January%2C%20when%20the%20protest%20rally%20was%20taken%20up%2C%20we%20registered%20another%20case%20under%20Section%20353%20against%20unknown%20persons%20for%20pelting%20stones%2C%20at%20Mandya%20East%20Police%20Station.%20We%20have%20taken%20up%20another%20case%20of%20damage%20to%20public%20property%20at%20Mandya%20West%20Police%20Station%2C%E2%80%9D%20SP%20Yathish%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20no%20one%20has%20been%20arrested%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis