ctions%2C%20how%20to%20create%20inducements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%20created%20an%20authoritarian%2C%20absolutist%20and%20autocratic%20system%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20a%20fundamental%20constitutional%20legal%20question%20for%20which%20we%20have%20only%20received%20stunning%20silence%20for%20the%20last%2018-odd%20hours.%20Yesterday%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20assembly%2C%20where%20the%20whole%20world%20knows%20that%20the%20figures%20are%20roughly%2047%20or%2048%20majority%20and%20roughly%2033%20or%2032%20opposition.%20After%20the%20honourable%20chief%20minister%20had%20submitted%20his%20resignation%20to%20the%20governor%20and%20a%20new%20chief%20minister%20with%20the%20numbers%20known%20was%20proposed%2C%20why%20has%20the%20governor%20been%20paralysed%20into%20inaction%20for%20the%20last%2018%20hours%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinghvi%20said%20that%20while%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20sworn%20in%20within%20hours%2C%20in%20Jharkhand%20there%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Csilence%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHardly%20a%20week%20ago%20in%20neighbouring%20Bihar%20where%20the%20borders%20touch%2C%20how%20quickly%20did%20the%20governor%20swear-in%20honourable%20Mr%20Paltu%20Kumar%20for%20the%20ninth%20time.%20How%20much%20time%20did%20it%20take%3F%20A%20few%20seconds%20a%20few%20minutes%20versus%2018%20hours%20till%20today%20as%20we%20speak%3F%20What%20kind%20of%20Einstein%E2%80%99s%20formula%20arithmetic%20is%20the%20governor%20trying%20to%20apply%20given%20to%20him%20from%20the%20self-evident%20fact%20given%20to%20him%20in%20writing%20with%20signatures.%2048%20versus%2032%20or%2047%20versus%2033%3F%20What%20is%20the%20explanation%20for%20this%20delay%3F%20Are%20you%20waiting%20for%20instructions%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%3F%20Or%20are%20you%20waiting%20for%20every%20possible%20way%20to%20get%20MLAs%20to%20change%20sides%20and%20do%20horse%20trading%3F%20Because%20this%20is%20your%20vision%20of%20New%20India%20of%20Amrit%20Kal%3F%20Are%20you%20waiting%20to%20impose%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20to%20remove%20a%20democratically%20elected%20government%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Soren%20tendered%20his%20resignation%20to%20the%20Jharkhand%20governor%20on%20Wednesday%20night%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20announced%20senior%20party%20leader%20and%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20transport%20minister%2C%20Champai%20Soren%2C%20as%20leader%20of%20the%20JMM%E2%80%99s%20legislative%20party%20and%20said%20that%20he%20is%20set%20to%20replace%20Hemant%20Soren%20as%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20coalition%20led%20by%20the%20JMM%20enjoys%20a%20majority%20of%2049%20legislators%20in%20the%2081-member%20assembly%2C%20including%2029%20from%20the%20JMM%2C%2016%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20one%20from%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20one%20from%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist-Leninist)%20Liberation%20(CPI(ML)L)%20and%20one%20from%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20legislators%20are%20reportedly%20unanimous%20in%20choosing%20Champai%20Soren%20to%20replace%20Hemant%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHemant%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20which%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20using%20probe%20agencies%20against%20opposition%20parties%20and%20becoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjharkhand-cm-hemant-soren-arrest-likely-ed%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ccourtiers%20in%20the%20court%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20tribal%20rights%20organisations%20in%20Jharkhand%20have%20also%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fjharkhand-bandh-today-tribal-outfits-call-shutdown-after-hemant-sorens-arrest-in-land-fraud-case-10-up