ndard.com%2Famp%2Fbudget%2Fnews%2Fbudget-2024-here-s-what-fm-nirmala-sitharaman-said-about-income-tax-124020100408_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Last%20Budget%20Before%20Elections%2C%20A%20Ram%20Mandir%20Mention%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Interim%20Budget%20for%202024%2C%20being%20presented%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20also%20saw%20a%20mention%20of%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Listing%20out%20the%20expected%20benefits%20of%20the%20rooftop%20solarisation%20programme%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20scheme%20is%20being%20implemented%20following%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20%26quot%3Bresolve%26quot%3B%20to%20do%20so%20after%20the%20historic%20ceremony%20on%20January%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20to%20New%20Delhi%20from%20Ayodhya%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20indicated%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20realisation%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20devotees%20of%20the%20world%20get%20energy%20from%20the%20light%20of%20Suryavanshi%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20decision%20I%20have%20taken%20after%20returning%20from%20Ayodhya%20is%20that%20our%20government%20will%20launch%20'Pradhanmantri%20Suryodaya%20Yojana'%20with%20the%20target%20of%20installing%20rooftop%20solar%20on%201%20crore%20houses.%20This%20will%20not%20only%20reduce%20the%20electricity%20bill%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20middle%20class%2C%20but%20also%20make%20India%20self-reliant%20in%20the%20field%20of%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20her%20sixth%20straight%20Budget%20speech%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThrough%20rooftop%20solarisation%2C%20one%20crore%20households%20will%20be%20enabled%20to%20obtain%20up%20to%20300%20units%20free%20electricity%20every%20month.%20This%20scheme%20follows%20the%20resolve%20of%