is%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20LIVE%20COVERAGE%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-budget-2024-live-updates-budget-2024-interim-budget-budget-nirmala-sitharaman-finance-minister-fm-income-tax-slab-income-tax-new-regime-income-t-4970811%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENirmala%20Sitharaman's%202024%20Interim%20Budget%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20full%20Union%20Budget%20will%20likely%20be%20presented%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20that%20tax%20slabs%20will%20stay%20the%20same%20will%20disappoint%20salaried%20taxpayers%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20had%20been%20hoping%20for%20cuts%20to%20help%20deal%20with%20perennial%20cost-of-living%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20significant%20point%20for%20taxpayers%20is%20that%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20both%20the%20old%20and%20new%20tax%20regimes%20will%20continue%2C%20meaning%20people%20can%20choose%20between%20them%20when%20filing%20their%20returns.%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20also%20touched%20on%20the%20introduction%20of%20new%20forms%20and%20software%20to%20make%20filing%20easier%20and%20simpler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Finterim-budget-2024-huge-investments-for-lakshadweep-to-draw-tourists-nirmala-sitharaman-4972065%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuge%20Investments%20For%20Lakshadweep%20To%20Draw%20Tourists%3A%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20processing%20time%20of%20tax%20returns%20have%20been%20reduced%20from%2093%20days%20in%202014%20to%20just%2010%20days%20this%20year%2C%20thereby%20making%20refunds%20faster%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cem%3EViksit%20%3C%2Fem%3EBharat%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresenting%20her%20sixth%20straight%20(but%20first%20interim)%20budget%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20also%20said