ng%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20sent%20them%20the%20synopsis%20of%20the%20lecture%20almost%20a%20month%20ago.%20The%20discussion%20over%20this%20started%20about%20four%20to%20five%20months%20ago%20and%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20deliberations%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20Jan%2031%20was%20finalised%20for%20the%20talk.%20The%20book%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20speak%20about%20is%20published%20and%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20I%20do%20not%20think%20this%20has%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20the%20content%20of%20the%20book%20or%20the%20topic%20of%20the%20lecture%2C%20nor%20do%20I%20wish%20to%20build%20a%20hypothesis%20around%20it.%20They%20are%20a%20scientific%20organisation%2C%20and%20I%20would%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20reasons%20are%20not%20irrational%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fdifficult-to-understand-why-iit-b-lecture-was-cancelled%2Farticleshow%2F107307803.cms%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20keynote%20speaker%20at%20IIT-Guwahati%E2%80%99s%20Graduate%20Research%20Meet%20in%20October%20last%20year%20and%20spoke%20on%20%E2%80%98Describing%20India%3A%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movements%20and%20Knowledge%20Production%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20the%20first%20lecture%20cancelled%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%20had%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiit-bombay-cancels-conference-left-education-ministry%5C%22%3Ecancelled%20a%20lecture%20titled%20%E2%80%98Israel-Palestine%3A%20The%20Historical%20Context%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Professor%20Achin%20Vanaik%20in%20November%20last%20year%20as%20well%20as%20a%20two-day%20conference%20on%20Left%20politics%20titled%20%E2%80%98Cultures%20of%20the%20Political%20Left%20in%20Modern%20India%E2%80%99%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20lecture%20on%20the%20Is