tv%2Fglobal%2Fveronika-crime-series-alexandra-rapaport-cast-trailer-skyshowtime-1235892781%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fveronika-crime-series-alexandra-rapaport-cast-trailer-skyshowtime-1235892781%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Gateway%20to%20Censorship'%3A%20Journalist%20Bodies%20Express%20Concern%20Over%20Proposed%20Broadcasting%20Services%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F11175411%2Fcensored.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJournalist%20bodies%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0The%20National%20Alliance%20of%20Journalists%20(NAJ)%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20(DUJ)%2C%20and%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Working%20Journalists%20Federation%20(APWJF)%20join%20the%20Network%20of%20Women%20in%20Media%20India%2C%20(NWMI)%20and%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20and%20others%20%E2%80%93%20have%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cgrave%20reservations%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20proposed%20Broadcasting%20Services%20(Regulation)%20Bill%202023.%20They%20describe%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgateway%20to%20censorship%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0In%20a%20joint%20statement%20the%20NAJ%2C%20DUJ%2C%20and%20APWJF%20say%20that%20this%20proposed%20Bill%20is%20a%20step%20further%20%E2%80%9Cto%20expanding%20a%20new%20era%20of%20undeclared%20censorship%E2%80%9D%20and%20increasing%20government%20control%20over%20all%20types%20of%20media%20from%20TV%20channels%2C%20to%20films%2C%20and%20platforms%20like%20Netflix%20and%20Prime%20Video%2C%20YouTube%2C%20radio%2C%20even%20Instagram%20and%20other%20social%20media%20platforms%20as%20well%20as%20news%20websites%20and%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Broadcasting%20Services%20(Regulation)%20Bill%2C%202023%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20Telecom%20Act%20of%202023%2C%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202023%2C%20and%20the%20IT%20Amendment%20Rules%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20Broadcasting%20Bill%20blurs%20the%20distinction%20between%20journalism%20and%20content%20creation.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20definition%20of%20news%20and%20current%20affair%20has%20been%20deliberately%20left%20so%20broad%20that%20all%20sorts%20of%20online%20media%20can%20be%20controlled%20through%20it.%20It%20clubs%20together%20both%20broadcast%20and%20digital%20media%2C%20although%20broadcast%20media%20includes%20the%20big%20channels%20while%20digital%20news%20media%20channels%20are%20often%20small%20outfits%20run%20by%20one%20or%20two%20persons.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20clauses%2C%20particularly%20those%20relating%20to%20self-censorship%2C%20are%20completely%20impractical%20given%20the%20nature%20of%20small%20news%20media.%20Some%20dangerous%20clauses%20include%20the%20power%20to%20seize%20electronic%20devices%20including%20studio%20equipment.%20There%20are%20apprehensions%20that%20the%20Bill%20could%20muffle%20independent%20voices%20including%20those%20of%20YouTube%20journalists%2C%20news%20analysts%20and%20digital%20websites.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20alternative%2C%20the%20journalist%20outfits%20say%20such%20a%20Bill%20could%20wait%20till%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20common%20body%20like%20a%20Media%20Commission%20of%20India%20comprising%20experts%20and%20stakeholders%20who%20could%20look%20into%20all%20aspects%20of%20self%20regulation%20rather%20than%20inviting%20government%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20there%20exists%20a%20wide%20spectrum%20media%2C%20ranging%20from%20print%2C%20broadcast%2C%20digital%20to%20TV%20and%20other%20media%20and%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20regulate%20it%20through%20such%20measures.%20Instead%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20organise%20extensive%20consultations%20with%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20look%20into%20the%20common%20grievances%E2%80%99%20and%20seek%20common%20solutions.%20Decisions%20made%20without%20democratic%20consultations%20could%20smack%20of%20authoritarianism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20allege%20that%20the%20Broadcast%20Bill%20%E2%80%9Cis%20being%20pushed%20in%20a%20hurry%20and%20could%20be%20yet%20another%20attempt%20to%20curb%20independent%20thinking%2C%20protest%20and%20dissent.%20It%20should%20be%20immediately%20rolled%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Bill%20is%20ominously%2C%20inexplicably%20silent%20on%20the%20concentration%20of%20media%20ownership%20in%20big%20corporate%20hands%20which%20is%20itself%20a%20big%20threat%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20diversity%20of%20opinion%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706767145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F11175411%2Fcensored.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgateway-to-censorship-journalist-bodies-express-concern-over-proposed-broadcasting-services-bill%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Alliance%20of%20Journalists%2C%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Working%20Journalists%20Federation%2C%20Network%20of%20Women%20in%20Media%20India%2C%20and%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20called%20it%20a%20step%20further%20'to%20expanding%20a%20new%20era%20of%20undeclared%20censorship'%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgateway-to-censorship-journalist-bodies-express-concern-over-proposed-broadcasting-services-bill%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canadian%20police%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20500-pound%20taxidermy%20polar%20bear%20stolen%20from%20a%20resort%20in%20frigid%2C%20below-zero%20weather%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22976%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harry%20the%20stuffed%20polar%20bear%20atop%20his%20platform.%5C%22%2