20them%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccreating%20tension%20and%20hatred.%E2%80%9D%20Suranya%20had%20allegedly%20noted%20in%20a%20Facebook%20video%20that%20she%20would%20go%20on%20a%20three-day%20fast%20to%20protest%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20built%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20%E2%80%93%20demolished%20by%20%3Cem%3Ekar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Esevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201992%20%E2%80%93%20once%20stood.%20It%20is%20this%20move%20that%20the%20RWA%20has%20taken%20exception%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20north%20India%2C%20RWAs%20had%20been%20active%20in%20getting%20residents%20to%20celebrate%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20the%20temple%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuranya%20has%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20the%20house%20is%20wholly%20owned%20by%20her%20father%2C%20a%20Congress%20leader%2C%20and%20that%20she%20does%20not%20live%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Facebook%2C%20she%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20going%20to%20try%20and%20avoid%20a%20media%20circus%20as%20I%20believe%20that%20we%20all%20in%20India%20deserve%20better.%20Let%20us%20stop%20abusing%20each%20other%20and%20try%20some%20thinking%20instead.%20Jai%20Hind!%E2%80%9D%20She%20has%20also%20released%20two%20video%20messages%2C%20in%20Hindi%20and%20English%2C%20to%20address%20reports%20on%20mainstream%20television%20media%20over%20the%20RWA%E2%80%99s%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuranya%20says%20that%20she%20is%2049%20years%20old%20and%20has%20lived%20in%20this%20country%20all%20her%20life%20and%20that%20she%20has%20worked%20in%20different%20fields%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20which%20is%20known%20to%20people.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20I%20hope%20that%20this%20gives%20everybody%20an%20opportunity%20to%20think%20about%20where%20we%20are%20going%2C%20and%20how%20we%20are%20going%20and%20whether%20we%20want%20to%20become%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%20which%20is%20signed%20by%20RWA%20president%20Kapil%20Kakar%2C%20the%20association%20has%20asked%20the%20duo%20to%20%E2%80%9Ckindly%20move%20out%20to%20another%20colony%2C%20where%20people%20and%20RWAs%20can%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20such%20hatred.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RWA%20has%20also%20asked%20Mani%20Shankar%20to%20condemn%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cact%E2%80%9D%20and%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Chate%20speech%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20might%20take%20the%20cover%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20but%20please%20remember%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20freedom%20of%20speech%20cannot%20be%20absolute%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20RWA%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20%E2%80%98IT-cell%E2%80%99%20chief%20Amit%20Malviya%20has%20posted%20on%20X%20saying%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cterse%20letter%E2%80%9D%20should%20%E2%80%9Cserve%20as%20a%20message%20for%20everyone%2C%20who%20think%20abusing%20Hindu%20beliefs%20is%20par%20for%20the%20course.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20questioned%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20RWA%E2%80%99s%20move%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterrifying%E2%80%9D%20example%20of%20%E2%80%9CNew%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20have%20dismissed%20it%20(the%20incident)%20as%20laughable%20were%20it%20not%20be%20tragic%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20only%20responding%20because%20these%20kind%20of%20incidents%20are%20tragic.%20I%20would%20never%20agree%20with%20you%20on%20a%20hundred%20issues.%20I%20may%20not%20agree%20with%20Mr%20Aiyar%20or%20his%20daughter%20on%20a%20hundred%20issues.%20But%20that%20is%20not%20the%20issue%20at%20all.%20How%20can%20I%20not%20allow%20your%20right%20to%20disagree%20with%20me%3F%20And%20what%20legality%20and%20constitutionality%20is%20there%20to%20ask%20him%20to%20get%20out%20of%20his%20colony%20because%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20what%20he%20says%3F%20This%20is%20terrifying%20in%20new%20India.%20He%20has%20the%20full%20right%20to%20disagree%20but%20can%20one%20neighbour%20tell%20the%20other%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhome-ministry-cancels-centre-for-policy-researchs-fcra-registration%5C%22%3Ecancelled%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20Regulation%20Act%20(FCRA)%20registration%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%2C%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20another%20one%20of%20Mani%20Shankar%E2%80%99s%20daughters%2C%20Yamini%20Aiyar.%20Academics%20and%20researchers%20from%20across%20the%20world%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdangerous-precedent-international-scholars-researchers-on-cprs-fcra-suspension%5C%22%3Ecriticised%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706757918000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01085050%2FUntitled-design-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmani-shankar-aiyar-suranya-jangpura-residents-welfare-association-rwa%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suranya%20has%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20the%20house%20is%20wholly%20owned%20by%20her%20father%2C%20a%20Congress%20leader%2C%20and%20that%20she%20does%20not%20live%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmani-shankar-aiyar-suranya-jangpura-residents-welfare-association-rwa%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20%2450%20billion%20Tesla%20pay%20was%20struck%20down.%20What%20happens%20next%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706757879000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107309727%2Cimgsize-1348138.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindi