ext%5C%22%3EInstalling%20the%20statue%20at%20Rajkot%2C%20Malvan%2C%20November%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Jaideep%20Apte%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20however%20unprecedented%20was%20that%20the%20commissioning%2C%20fabrication%20and%20installation%20of%20this%20monument%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaharashtratimes.com%2Fmaharashtra%2Fsindhudurg%2Fkalyan-sculpture-jaydeep-apte-sculpts-chhatrapati-shivaji-maharaj-statue-unveiled-by-pm-narendra-modi-in-sindhudurg-malvan-rajkot-fort%2Farticleshow%2F105769632.cms%5C%22%3Ecarried%20out%20with%20deep%20involvement%20of%20Naval%20officers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20an%20uncanny%20understanding%20of%20the%20political%20alignments%20of%20aesthetics%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20expansive%20knowledge%20of%20implementing%20a%20project%20with%20military%20precision.%20Once%20cast%2C%20the%20sculpture%20was%20transported%20in%20a%20truck%20and%20assembled%20on%20site%20just%20a%20few%20days%20before%20its%20consecration%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20for%20security%20reasons%20apparently%2C%20local%20skilled%20workers%20had%20a%20minimal%20role%20to%20play%20in%20scouting%20the%20site%2C%20with%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20the%20work%20being%20outsourced%20to%20men%20in%20uniform%20from%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Dockyards%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20Naval%20ships%20are%20repaired%20and%20maintained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacts%20and%20fiction%20have%20often%20been%20mingled%20in%20contemporary%20interpretations%20of%20the%20life%20and%20times%20of%20the%20Maratha%20king%2C%20which%20have%20been%20delved%20into%20by%20several%20writers%20in%20the%20past.%20However%2C%20my%20interest%20lies%20in%20something%20else%2C%20rather%20than%20another%20exploration%20of%20his%20historical%20legacy.%20What%20needs%20to%20be%20analysed%20is%20how%20a%20granular%20public%20memory%20is%20being%20pulverised%20and%20reconstituted%20through%20a%20vast%20digital%20operating%20system%2C%20to%20consolidate%20the%20visual%20field%20into%20a%20monocultural%20world%20view.%20Enough%20studies%20have%20been%20done%20on%20how%20political%20systems%20mobilise%20mass%20adulation%20through%20monumental%20statuary%20and%20marking%20of%20physical%20sites.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20era%20of%20social%20media%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20be%20attentive%20to%20how%20memory%20is%20being%20modified%20through%20the%20technical%20dominance%20of%20official%20image%20dispersion%20methodologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunity%20memories%20of%20the%20Malvan%20event%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20have%20coalesced%20around%20the%20spectacular%20images%20put%20out%20by%20the%20government%20propaganda%20machinery%2C%20shot%20with%20high-end%20equipment%20of%20official%20photographers%20on%20duty%20and%20taken%20from%20unmatched%20viewing%20angles%20that%20only%20they%20had%20access%20to.%20My%20quest%20for%20images%20of%20the%20Navy%20Day%20%E2%80%98Operational%20Demonstration%E2%80%99%20taken%20by%20local%20residents%20a%20fortnight%20after%20the%20event%20yielded%20no%20results%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%20I%20was%20repeatedly%20directed%20to%20online%20repositories%20of%20official%20photographers%20by%20people%20who%20had%20nonetheless%20personally%20witnessed%20the%20events%2C%20even%20if%20from%20afar.%20Neither%20the%20local%20newspaper%20and%20not%20even%20the%20Malvan%20BJP%20office%20could%20give%20me%20access%20to%20photographs%20taken%20by%20their%20associates%2C%20even%20though%20they%20were%20listed%20as%20key%20organisers%20of%20the%20event%20in%20news%20stories%20that%20came%20out%20locally.%20A%20visit%20to%20three%20photo%20studios%20in%20town%2C%20who%20run%20a%20thriving%20business%20of%20wedding%20photography%20and%20passport%20photographs%2C%20also%20turned%20up%20a%20blank.%20On%20probing%20further%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20people%20who%20did%20take%20photographs%20had%2C%20not%20surprisingly%2C%20deleted%20them%20from%20their%20phones.%20For%20mobile%20phone%20photographs%20take%20up%20too%20much%20digital%20memory%20space%20and%20for%20many%2C%20they%20seem%20to%20be%20nothing%20more%20than%20an%20elongated%20pause%20of%20a%20fleeting%20moment%2C%20unless%20photography%20is%20their%20professional%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20sculpture%20was%20unveiled%20last%20December%2C%20the%20entire%20space%20around%20the%20site%20and%20staged%20ceremonies%20had%20been%C2%A0%20cordoned%20off%2C%20with%20views%20of%20what%20transpired%20made%20available%20for%20all%20only%20via%20officially%20mandated%20news%20outlets.%20The%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20now%20the%20most%20subscribed%20in%20the%20world%20of%20any%20political%20leader%2C%20has%20been%20very%20active%20since%20then%20in%20disseminating%20information%20about%20the%20event%20and%20his%20performative%20politics.%20No%20political%20leader%20in%20contemporary%20times%20has%20a%20better%20grasp%20of%20how%20ceremonial%20protocols%2C%20invented%20and%20performed%20for%20image%20enhancement%20and%20amplified%20via%20social%20media%2C%20work.%20The%20rituals%20are%20carefully%20choreographed%20for%20aura%20building%2C%20where%20distancing%20and%20staged%20proximity%20with%20the%20members%20of%20the%20public%20are%20of%20equal%20importance%2C%20as%20is%20their%20dispersal%20through%20a%20tightly%20controlled%20media%20that%20play%20out%20snippets%20of%20these%20performances%2C%20a%20manifestation%20of%20the%C2%A0%20biopolitical%20state%20that%20India%20has%20become%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-wBsBZGYTiE%3Fsi%3D4VsyjdDg_olAOpOS%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20uncanny%20how%20there%20is%20little%20left%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20digital%20trace%20in%20the%20expanded%20memory%20of%20the%20local%20residents.%C2%A0%20Speaking%20to%20my%20network%20of%20acquaintances%20revealed%20that%20as%20they%20watched%20the%20spectacular%20events%20unfold%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20their%20hand-held%20mobile%20phone%20cameras%20could%20not%20capture%20the%20blinding%20light%20of%20exploding%20bombs%2C%20contrails%20of%20fighter%20aircrafts%C2%A0%20and%20whirring%20helicopters%20above%20that%20were%20the%20mainstay%20of%20the%20Naval%20power%20display.%20The%20millions%20of%20views%20that%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20pages%20get%20have%20simply%20overpowered%20images%20taken%20with%20poor%20grade%20phone%20cameras%20that%20the%20second%20hand%20economy%20of%20phones%20available%20in%20the%20local%20mobile%20phone%20shops%20makes%20possible.%20The%20more%20expensive%20phone%20cameras%20do%20not%20make%20their%20way%20into%20the%20local%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%20though%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20some%20images%20from%20a%20member%20of%20the%20public%20who%20did%20witness%20the%20events%20and%20had%20access%20to%20a%20better-quality%20camera%20phone.%20The%20images%20taken%20by%20him%20reveal%20paratroopers%20landing%20on%20the%20beach%20front%2C%C2%A0%20flying%20the%20Indian%20tricolour%20in%20a%20mock%20display%20of%20a%20sea%20front%20confrontation%20with%20an%20imaginary%20enemy.%20Another%20reveals%20a%20fireball%20in%20the%20shallow%20waters%20of%20the%20sea%2C%20brought%20about%20by%20what%20looks%20like%C2%A0%20a%20drone%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20shooting%20at%20a%20ground%20level%20target.%20A%20fly-past%20as%20well%20punctures%20the%20sky.%20It%20certainly%20appears%20that%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20is%20well%20prepared%20for%20any%20threats%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20integrity%2C%20as%20long%20as%20environmental%20concerns%20are%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(